---
By: Paramananda
Locus:
  Page: 153
  Verse: 20
Tags:
  - Faith
---
The idea of faith is often misunderstood by people, because they associate
it with those who are ignorant, uneducated, and who have no power to
investigate for themselves. But faith is not blind belief. It is never
well-founded until it is based on experience.
